LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       H_16.lmp
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (11 11.002 11)
  2 by 2 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  49 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.00769677 secs

timestep 0.25

# ---------- Define Interatomic Potential ---------------------
pair_style      reax/c NULL checkqeq no
pair_coeff      * * ffield.reax C H
fix             2 all qeq/reax 1 0.0 10.0 1.0e-6 reax/c

#------------ Equilibration of the system -------------------------
reset_timestep 0

dump 1 all custom 10 min.lammpstrj id type x y z

